import numpy
import pandas
import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

import utils

优化Rosenbrock函数：

$f(x_0, x_1)=[10(x_1-x_0^2)^2]+(1-x_0)^2=100x_0^4+x_0^2-2x_0-200x_1x_0^2+100x_1^2+1$

梯度：

$\nabla f(x_0, x_1)=[400x_0^3+2x_0-400x_1x_0-2,\ \ 200x_1-200x_0^2]$

Hessian矩阵：

$ \nabla^2 f(x_0, x_1)= \left[ \begin{matrix}{} &1200x_0^2+2-400x_1, &-400x_0 &\\ &-400x_0, &200 & \end{matrix} \right]$

In [2]:
def func(x):
    # Rosenbrock函数
    return numpy.sum(numpy.array([10 * (x[1] - x[0]**2), (1 - x[0])])**2)

def gredient(x):
    # 梯度
    return numpy.array([400*x[0]**3+2*x[0]-400*x[1]*x[0]-2, 200*x[1]-200*x[0]**2])

def Hessian(x):
    # Hessian
    return numpy.array([[1200*x[0]**2+2-400*x[1], -400*x[0]],
                        [-400*x[0], 200]])

def is_pos_def(m):
    b = numpy.linalg.eigvals(m)
    if numpy.all(b > 0):
        return True
    return False

def plot_heatmap(x):
    x_in_archor = archor_list[utils.closest_point(archor_list, x.reshape((1,-1)))].reshape(-1)
    mask = numpy.all(numpy.array([archors[1,:,:]==x_in_archor[1], archors[0,:,:]==x_in_archor[0]]), axis=0).T
    sns.set()
    ax = sns.heatmap(value_map_pd, xticklabels="auto", yticklabels="auto", mask=mask)
    plt.show()
In [36]:
f_trace = []
x_trace = []
eps = 0.1
u=1
x=numpy.array([0,9])
g = gredient(x)
G = Hessian(x)
f0 = func(x)
q0 = f0 
f_trace.append(f0)
x_trace.append(x)
plot_heatmap(x)
while(True):
    if numpy.sum(numpy.abs(g)) < eps:
        break
    Gu = G + u*numpy.eye(G.shape[0])
    while(not is_pos_def(Gu)):
        u = u*4
        Gu = G + u*numpy.eye(G.shape[0])
    s = -numpy.matmul(numpy.linalg.inv(Gu),g)
    f = func(x+s)
    f_trace.append(f)
    x_trace.append(x)
    plot_heatmap(x)
    q = f + numpy.dot(g,s) + 0.5*numpy.matmul(s.reshape(1,-1), numpy.matmul(G, s))
    r = (q0-q)/(f0-f)
    if r > 0:
        x = x + s
    if r < 0.25:
        u = u * 4
    elif r > 0.75:
        u = u / 2
    q0 = q
    f0 = f
    g = gredient(x)
    G = Hessian(x)
